  "title": "AB03 - Technician – Pest Management",
  "description": "<p><strong>Pest Control Technician</strong></p><p>Location: Tanjong Pagar</p><p>Working Days: 5.5 days</p><p>Working hours : 8am to 5pm, 8am to 12pm</p><p>Salary : $1,600 - $2,600 (depend on experience)</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>To ensure prompt and timely pest control service at customers’ premises</li><li>To provide good quality service to customers</li><li>To carry out pest inspections at customers’ premises</li><li>To submit a service report promptly</li><li>To maintain company equipment in good and working condition</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 1 - 2 years of Pest control experience</li><li>Possess NEA license  & Class 3 driving license (vehicle can discuss to drive back)</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
